metadata.name: Kinky Thoughts #1/50
metadata.description:
This work is one frame from my 7th work from the Endless Thoughts Collection. 
Endless Thoughts is the result of a year's effort and my first 3D collection.  
I created this collection by keeping the DNA of my works until today.  
The general theme is the negative thoughts and annoying feelings that we are stuck in our life experiences.  
My goal was to show that there is always a way to break free from these thoughts.  
The end of the endless cycle of these thoughts and maybe a window to another collection.
